function is advisable.', 'Synergism', 'The use of naltrexone with other potentially hepatotoxic agents should be avoided whenever possible (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/93775/', '', 'Maprotiline, Fluoxetine, St. John''s Wort, Vortioxetine, Levomilnacipran, Doxepin, Isocarboxazid, Viloxazine, Amoxapine, Imipramine, Esketamine, More', 'Naloxone, Nalmefene, Disulfiram', 1767369485);
